== 制作 ==
[[丹泽尔·华盛顿|丹泽尔·华盛顿]]最初与电视台[[HBO|HBO]]签订协议，将{{tsl|en|August Wilson|奥古斯特·威尔逊}}的九部剧作改编成电影，《蓝调天后》就是其中一部<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/denzel-washington-direct-august-wilson-824491|title=Denzel Washington to Direct August Wilson Play for HBO in Broad Deal|website=The Hollywood Reporter|first=Arlene|last=Washington|access-date=2021-02-04|date=2015-09-17|archive-date=2019-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190709194747/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/denzel-washington-direct-august-wilson-824491|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年6月，协议转至Netflix。[[维奥拉·戴维斯|维奥拉·戴维斯]]、[[查德維克·博斯曼|查德維克·博斯曼]]、{{tsl|en|Glynn Turman|格林·特曼}}、{{tsl|en|Colman Domingo|科尔曼·多明戈}}和{{tsl|en|Michael Potts (actor)|迈克尔·波兹}}出演，{{tsl|en|George C. Wolfe|乔治·C·沃尔夫}}执导<ref>{{cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2019/06/viola-davis-chadwick-boseman-netflix-movie-ma-raineys-black-bottom-august-wilson-1202635104/|title=Viola Davis, Chadwick Boseman & More to Star in Denzel Washington Netflix Pic Adaptation Of August Wilson's 'Ma Rainey's Black Bottom'|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|website=Deadline Hollywood|access-date=2021-02-04|date=2019-06-19|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031212947/https://deadline.com/2019/06/viola-davis-chadwick-boseman-netflix-movie-ma-raineys-black-bottom-august-wilson-1202635104/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年7月，{{tsl|en|Taylour Paige|泰勒·佩奇}}、{{tsl|en|Jonny Coyne|乔尼·科恩}}、{{tsl|en|Jeremy Shamos|杰里米·沙莫斯}}和杜尚·布朗加入剧组<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/07/ma-raineys-black-bottom-taylour-paige-jonny-coyne-denzel-washington-august-wilson-netflix-1202641389/|title='Ma Rainey's Black Bottom': Taylour Paige, Jonny Coyne & More Join Denzel Washington-Produced August Wilson Adaptation|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|date=2019-07-02|access-date=2019-07-02|archive-date=2019-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190702232327/https://deadline.com/2019/07/ma-raineys-black-bottom-taylour-paige-jonny-coyne-denzel-washington-august-wilson-netflix-1202641389/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Maxayn Lewis|玛克西恩·刘易斯}}演唱戴维斯为雷尼演唱的大部分歌曲<ref>{{cite news|title=How Branford Marsalis Found Ma Rainey's Sound|url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2020/12/ma-raineys-black-bottom-branford-marsalis-interview|last=Hoffman|first=Jordan|date=2020-12-18|access-date=2020-12-28|work=Vanity Fair|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231034139/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2020/12/ma-raineys-black-bottom-branford-marsalis-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年7月8日，摄制工作在匹兹堡进行，片场改造成1927年的芝加哥。2019年8月16日杀青<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.post-gazette.com/ae/movies/2019/07/01/Ma-Rainey-film-August-Wilson-Pittsburgh-exteriors-North-Side-Denzel/stories/201907010099|title=August Wilson's 'Ma Rainey's Black Bottom' prepping exteriors on Pittsburgh's North Side|website=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette|first=Maria|last=Sciullo|date=2019-07-01|access-date=2019-07-02|archive-date=2019-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190702232327/https://www.post-gazette.com/ae/movies/2019/07/01/Ma-Rainey-film-August-Wilson-Pittsburgh-exteriors-North-Side-Denzel/stories/201907010099|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

主演博斯曼在影片后期阶段的2020年8月去世，该片因此成了他的遗作，影片有向他致敬的画面<ref name="Grdn">{{cite news|last=Lee|first=Benjamin|title=Netflix releases trailer for Chadwick Boseman's final movie|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/oct/19/chadwick-boseman-final-movie-trailer-netflix|access-date=2020-10-24|work=The Guardian|date=2020-10-18|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024100742/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/oct/19/chadwick-boseman-final-movie-trailer-netflix|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.looper.com/241360/this-will-be-chadwick-bosemans-final-movie/|title=This will be Chadwick Boseman's final movie|work=Looper|first=Shane|last=O'Neill|date=2020-08-29|access-date=2020-08-29|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010221008/https://www.looper.com/241360/this-will-be-chadwick-bosemans-final-movie/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Chadwick Boseman pictured in Ma Rainey's Black Bottom - his last acting role before his death|url=https://news.sky.com/story/chadwick-boseman-pictured-in-ma-raineys-black-bottom-his-last-acting-role-before-his-death-12087303|first=Chris|last=Robertson|date=2020-10-01|access-date=2020-10-02|website=Sky News|archive-date=2020-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004095516/https://news.sky.com/story/chadwick-boseman-pictured-in-ma-raineys-black-bottom-his-last-acting-role-before-his-death-12087303|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 发行 ==
影片于2020年11月25日在指定影院上映<ref name="Grdn"/>，12月18日登陆Netflix<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/30/movies/chadwick-boseman-ma-raineys-black-bottom.html|title=First Look: Viola Davis and Chadwick Boseman in 'Ma Rainey's Black Bottom'|website=The New York Times|first=Kyle|last=Buchanan|date=2020-09-30|access-date=2020-09-30|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003002717/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/30/movies/chadwick-boseman-ma-raineys-black-bottom.html/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。幕后纪录片《蓝调天后：传奇再现》（''Ma Rainey's Black Bottom: A Legacy Brought to Screen''）同步上线<ref>{{cite web|last=Moore|first=Kasey|title=What's New on Netflix & Top 10s: December 18th, 2020|url=https://www.whats-on-netflix.com/whats-new/whats-new-on-netflix-top-10s-december-18th-2020/|website=What's on Netflix|access-date=2021-02-04|date=2020-12-18|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109003117/https://www.whats-on-netflix.com/whats-new/whats-new-on-netflix-top-10s-december-18th-2020/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。上线首周末，影片成为该站观看次数最多的影片<ref>{{cite news|date=2020-12-21|last=Brueggemann|first=Tom|title='The Croods: A New Age' Beats Out 'Tenet' On VOD in Surprising Shakeup|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/12/croods-a-new-age-beats-tenet-vod-1234606022/|website=IndieWire|access-date=2020-12-22|archive-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221225014/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/12/croods-a-new-age-beats-tenet-vod-1234606022/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

