=== 专业评价 ===
[[汇总媒体|汇总媒体]][[烂番茄|烂番茄]]收录评论283条，打出98%的新鲜度，平均得分8.2/10。网站共识写道：“在两位主角精彩演绎的加持下，《蓝调天后》深情致敬了一位蓝调传奇及整个黑人文化<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ma_raineys_black_bottom|title=Ma Rainey's Black Bottom (2020)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|access-date=2021-03-27|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127212202/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ma_raineys_black_bottom|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]收录46条评论，平均分87/100，表示“普遍好评”<ref>{{cite web|title=Ma Rainey's Black Bottom Reviews|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/ma-raineys-black-bottom|website=Metacritic|access-date=2021-01-17|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211102537/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/ma-raineys-black-bottom|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》专栏作家{{tsl|en|Justin Chang|贾斯汀·张}}表示：“整个职业生涯都保持高风亮节的博斯曼拒绝淡化影片的主旨，愤怒和苦痛驱使下，他将不完整的灵魂乐天赋，赐给了这位闷闷不乐、伤心难过的男士，让他为音乐投入更多真情实感。博斯曼在荧幕上的最后岁月，是他最黑暗的时刻，也是最美好的<ref>{{cite web|date=2020-11-20|last=Chang|first=Justin|title='Ma Rainey's Black Bottom' review: Chadwick Boseman's final and finest performance|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-11-20/review-ma-raineys-black-bottom-netflix-boseman-davis|work=Los Angeles Times|access-date=2020-11-20|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201060604/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-11-20/review-ma-raineys-black-bottom-netflix-boseman-davis|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]埃里克·科恩（Eric Kohn）打出“B”评级，赞扬博斯曼和戴维斯的表演：“《蓝调天后》如果能收敛一下威尔逊咿咿呀呀的对白，还有跟音乐并驾齐驱的爵士节奏，就会是一部更让人感同身受的作品。归根结底，影片可以归纳为一场坚定的复兴，没有堆砌夺人眼球的桥段<ref>{{cite news|last=Kohn|first=Eric|title='Ma Rainey's Black Bottom' Review: Boseman and Davis Energize a Faithful August Wilson Adaptation|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/11/ma-raineys-black-bottom-review-netflix-1234599878/|date=2020-11-20|work=IndieWire|access-date=2020-11-20|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120170224/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/11/ma-raineys-black-bottom-review-netflix-1234599878/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

[[ABC新闻|ABC新闻]]电影评论[[彼得·崔維斯|彼得·崔維斯]]指出：“戴维斯扮演了现实生活中的玛·雷尼，被封为‘蓝调之母’的乔治亚歌手。博斯曼全身心投入到莱维这个角色，这个头脑发热的小号手将吹给玛女士的号角声，深锁在破旧的芝加哥录音棚，花钱租下这个地方，遵照白人上司的旨意创作音乐。那是在1927年。但在种族关系剑拔弩张的当下，这部影片来得可谓非常及时<ref>{{cite news|last=Travers|first=Peter|title='Ma Rainey' review: The film, starring Viola Davis and Chadwick Boseman, is 'a gut punch'|url=https://www.goodmorningamerica.com/culture/story/ma-rainey-review-gut-punch-movie-knock-loop-74299929|date=2020-11-20|work=ABC News|access-date=2020-11-23|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123003020/https://www.goodmorningamerica.com/culture/story/ma-rainey-review-gut-punch-movie-knock-loop-74299929|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

